   <description url="https://www.cevelop.com/features">
      Elevator is a Plug-in for Eclipse CDT that helps refactor existing
C++ code towards the C++11 ISO standard. It currently provides
programmer assistance for migrating variable declarations and
initializations to the new uniform initialization syntax.
   </description>

